<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Action Required: Update Razorpay Details</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #333;">
    <h2>Hello <%= name %>,</h2>

    <p>
        This is a gentle reminder that your Razorpay <strong>Key ID</strong> and 
        <strong>Secret Key</strong> have not been added yet in your account.
    </p>

    <p>
        Your students are trying to pay their <strong>online fees</strong>, but the payment
        is failing because Razorpay details are missing.
    </p>

    <p>Please update your Razorpay keys as soon as possible to enable online fee collection.</p>

    <p>
        <a href="https://libtrack-demo.netlify.app/dashboard/settings" 
           style="background-color: #007bff; padding: 10px 20px; color: white; 
                  border-radius: 5px; text-decoration: none;">
            Update Razorpay Details
        </a>
    </p>

    <br/>

    <p>Thank you,<br/>Team Libtrack</p>
</body>
</html>
